      <title>Tech Tuesday Training: SharePoint Summer Camp: Camp Rules: SharePoint Permissions &amp; Sharing</title>
      <description><![CDATA[<div>  <img src="https://localist-images.azureedge.net/photos/52939115993558/huge/299aceb26bfd3123a58ee4753b613da1d4c81e97.jpg" style="width: 100%;" />  <div style="font-size: 0.9em; color: #555;"><strong>Tue, 23 Jun 2026</strong></div>  <div><p>Pack your virtual backpack and join ETS Training for SharePoint Summer Camp—a June-long, hands-on training series that helps you build strong SharePoint skills, one week at a time. No experience required—just curiosity and a willingness to learn.</p>

<p>June 23 – Camp Rules: SharePoint Permissions &amp; Sharing</p>

